news.Title: Parents of Liverpool winger Diaz kidnapped in Colombia
news.Description: The mother of Liverpool's Colombian winger Luis Diaz was rescued from kidnappers on Saturday but a search remains on for his father, Colombian President Gustavo Petro said on Saturday.
news.Summary: Bogotá (AFP) – The mother of Liverpool's Colombian winger Luis Diaz was rescued from kidnappers on Saturday but a search remains on for his father, Colombian President Gustavo Petro said on Saturday. The mother of Colombian footballer Luis Diaz, who plays for Liverpool of England, was rescued on October 28, 2023, after the authorities reported the kidnapping of his parents in the department of Guajira (north), said President Gustavo Petro.
